Title: One day at cafeteria
DateModified: '2019-02-28'
DatePublished: '2019-02-28'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/one-day-at-cafeteria
SetInCountry: India
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Md Jannisar  Akhter
AuthorCountry: India
Text: When I was at my school , I was very shy .one we planed for a school trip for
  Darjeeling with our school friends.when we reached in the city we had fun much and
  in the evening we were having a coffee .one of my friend her name was Riya came
  and told me I like you, I was totally stucked , I asked why  .she told me I think
  you always care me .And I told her ,i need some time to think about .when we came
  back to school, after two days , she died in car accident , I bought flowers and
  chocolates before her death , when  I heard this news .......I can't explain . I
  always miss her
